Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located in Greenscape, Cyber One, a premium building in Navi Mumbai. Perched on the 17th floor with bay windows on all sides and uninterrupted sea views from most of its offices, it offers a bright and well-lit ambience that provides plenty of space to think, work and stretch your imagination and legs.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Multiple co-working spaces available in a prime location at Cyber One

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
"Our Vashi, Sector 17 pro-working centre is in the commercial hub of Navi Mumbai surrounded by a dense concentration of small businesses, offices, clinics, banks, retail outlets and restaurants. This centre is closely located to the local station and is easily accessible via other public transport.

Our Office Space in Vashi has a total capacity of 356 workstations and 4 meeting rooms. The seating plan includes premium cabins, fixed desks and flexible desk arrangements. Our collaboration zone consists of meeting lounges, rock pods and provides you with the right activity based ambience fostering productivity. The fixed desk spaces and premium cabins offer pedestal storage, whiteboards and pin-up boards while flexible desk spaces are spread across a vibrant community table setup.

Our Co working Space in Vashi is completely secure with entry allowed only through NFC based access cards and has CCTV coverage. Our members have access to hi-tech infrastructure facilities that include Video Projection, Video Conferencing, High Speed Internet and Laser Printing.

Depending on membership plans, members get complimentary Meeting Credits which can be redeemed across meeting rooms in any Awfis location. Members also get Tea/Coffee and Printing Credits on a complimentary basis. Parking Facilities can also be availed by members. Centre Pantry also has a wide menu of Food and beverage offered at very reasonable pricing. Our on-site community managers and centre team is available to help you with any requirements. We offer options to work beyond office hours and on public holidays.

We offer ease of just-in-time booking through Awfis mobile app. Renewing the shared workspaces as well as private cabins is also hassle-free. Every member also gets an access to Awfis Alliances program, where preferential offers from leading merchants have been curated specially for Awfis Community. Once you have experienced working at Awfis, it will change the way you think about collaborative working."

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Multiple co-working spaces available in a prime location of Navi Mumbai

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Innov8 Fairmount Sector 17, Sanpada is located at one of Navi Mumbai’s most promising localities. Being Innov8’s first coworking space in Sanpada, Navi Mumbai, this center is beautifully designed and offers office space, shared offices, desk space, dedicated desk, meeting rooms, event spaces at very affordable prices. The location is set just before the Palm Beach Road, a premium district for your business. The centre directly overlooks the Thane Creek with stunning views of the Arabian Sea & having perfect setting for unwinding after a hefty day at work. You can view acres of the green plush trees spread along with the Sea. Therefore, If you’re looking for a fully-equipped coworking space for rent in Sanpada, Navi Mumbai, Then look nowhere else other than Innov8 Fairmount, the best office space for rent in Sanpada, Navi Mumbai.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Innov8 Fairmount - Vibrant workspaces with multiple F&B options, event spaces, meeting spaces and unmatched services, with stunning sea views, located in Sanpada, Navi Mumbai, very close to two railway stations
